heading: Speedfarming Builds Tier List
content: This tier list compares all Endgame builds in easy farming content such as lower once they have reached their maximum potential and been optimized in the lategame. Mobility, AoE damage and the ability to take down moderately tanky bosses play the largest part in whether a build is considered high tier.
